input_text.Prompt:
Given a item title and item features, this program will generate exciting product descriptions.

Item title:
Rothco P/T Marines T-Shirt

Item features:
100% Polyester
Quality tested and ensured for maximum durability
Designed with only the toughest, roughest users in mind
Comfort and Performance come hand in hand with Rothco

Product description:
input_text.Response A: Are you a marine? Do you want to feel like one? Get the Rothco PT Marines T-Shirt and show your pride. This t-shirt is designed with only the toughest, roughest users in mind. It's made from 100% polyester and is quality tested and ensured for maximum durability. With Rothco, you know that comfort and performance come hand in hand. So whether you're in the field or just out for a hike, this t-shirt will keep you comfortable and looking good.
input_text.Response B: Rothco P/T Marines T-Shirt is a performance shirt designed for the toughest, roughest users in mind. The P/T Marines T-Shirt is made of 100% polyester and is designed for maximum durability. The comfort and performance come hand in hand with Rothco.
